column5: Headin down to Thunder-Bay tommorrow and was gonna try for a few hours on the big lake. See if I can ice some steel!!! Anyone with an update on conditions???
cant help ya with the ice question, but just thoiught i'd say hi, been a while!

The harbor and areas along the lake heading south were ice covered as of yesterday. No idea how thick it was and I did not see much indication of recent fishing activity there....I guess Im not much help

...Hello my good man. See you have managed a couple out of 'eagle', good on ya. We gotta try to get out once again before the ice is out...I'll be back this way For A sunday fish if you goits any ideas. Upper Manitou?????
I work tonight and Sunday night, but if we leave here early Sunday Morning and get back by 2pm i'''d be good for Manitou
